            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crush the <strong>cardamom pods</strong> open by squashing them with the side of a knife</p><p>Heat a pot with a lid, with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a large knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once the butter has melted, add the <strong>crushed cardamom</strong> and <strong>basmati rice</strong> and stir to fully coat the grains</p>",
